# Reclaim Org Vision

- **Core vision**: A world where humanity reclaims its digital destiny, dismantling the temples of algorithmic manipulation built by profit-obsessed giants. No longer reduced to data points in the spreadsheets of the powerful, people co-own and co-create their digital spaces. The digital realm becomes a canvas for the Übermensch — self-directed, co-governed, and freed from the tyranny of surveillance and advertising. In this world, content is not commodified; it is forged by the will to power and shared in the light of creative authenticity.

- **Product implication**:
  - Design Reclaim as a co-owned, user-empowering space, not an extractive platform.
  - Avoid dark patterns, manipulative engagement tricks, or ad-style language.
  - Emphasize autonomy, creative agency, and resistance to surveillance in copy and flows.
  - Highlight "reclaiming your digital destiny" and "co-owning your creative space" in marketing and UX narratives.

